Time & Space Complexity of Linear Queue    (Array Implementation)


Particulars     | Time Complexity | Space Complexity |
createQueue()   |   O(1)          |     O(n)         |
enQueue()       |   O(1)          |     O(1)         |
Dequeue()       |   O(1)          |     O(1)         |
peek()          |   O(1)          |     O(1)         |
IsEmpty()       |   O(1)          |     O(1)         |
IsFull()        |   O(1)          |     O(1)         |
deleteQueue()   |   O(1)          |     O(1)         |

